The halfling mask Overseer is in the mines. If you go to Niblik and just keep following the wall to the right, you will get to a room with a building in it. There is a tunnel to the right there, so keep following the right wall. The next spawns include the Foreman (I think always, but not sure), and after that there is a 'T' in the hallway - this is where the Overseer or his PH spawns. Best I can do from memory and I hope it helps, but if this doesn' t I'll look at a map and describe it better if you want <img src="images/smilies/smile.gif" border="0" alt=""><FONT face="arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF"><br>
